</p></entry><entry colname="col5" namest="col5" nameend="col6" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> As the UI was presumed to show information from the windows controller before switching the cable, it is assumed that the Graphics part of the EC controller is not functioning correctly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See: <ph varid="SPP-COLO_M-SERIES_BASE-Z-2103" class="- topic/ph ">
          <xref href="PRT-SPP-COLO_M-SERIES_BASE-2103.xml" scope="external" type="extpl" format="html" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>Z-2103</xref>
