</p></entry><entry colname="col5" namest="col5" nameend="col6" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The EC controller can be in a deep sleep state. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The controller can exit the sleep state by creating a shortcut between Pin 1 and Pin 2 on the power supply of the controller as indicated in the image below: 
</p><fig id="GUID-B0FD09E7-21B4-4E90-9D41-501621E7C0A4" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-1A94554F-5C92-4E8D-8ECF-47E021BA18C6-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1A94554F-5C92-4E8D-8ECF-47E021BA18C6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">31 
